    "text": "Khi đó: $\\cos(\\vec{u}, \\vec{v}) = \\frac{\\vec{u} \\cdot \\vec{v}}{|\\vec{u}| \\cdot |\\vec{v}|} \\Leftrightarrow \\cos 60^{\\circ} = \\frac{1-m\\sqrt{2}}{2\\sqrt{1+m^2}} \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{1-m\\sqrt{2}}{2\\sqrt{1+m^2}} = \\frac{1}{2} \\Leftrightarrow 2(1-m\\sqrt{2}) = 2\\sqrt{1+m^2}$\n$\\Leftrightarrow 1-m\\sqrt{2} = \\sqrt{1+m^2} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} 1-m\\sqrt{2} \\ge 0 \\\\ (1-m\\sqrt{2})^2 = 1+m^2 \\end{cases} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} m \\le \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}} \\\\ 1-2m\\sqrt{2}+2m^2 = 1+m^2 \\end{cases} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} m \\le \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}} \\\\ m^2-2m\\sqrt{2}=0 \\end{cases}$\n$\\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} m \\le \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}} \\\\ m=0 \\\\ m=2\\sqrt{2} \\end{cases} \\Leftrightarrow m = 2\\sqrt{2}.$"
